<p>Students have approached members of the Student Representative Council to express their desire to know BYU-Idaho's stance on same gender attraction. The SRC has identified church and campus resources for those dealing with same gender attraction. All students who struggle or wish to help friends or roommates are encouraged to understand the church's position on same-gender attraction by reading the Church's official Web site: <a href="http://www.lds.org/topics/same-gender-attraction">www.lds.org/topics/same-gender-attraction</a>.</p>
<p>"Resources have been made available for students to privately discuss such sensitive issues as same-gender attraction and homosexual behavior. Campus ecclesiastical leaders and the Counseling Center provide students with safe, confidential venues to talk openly about and receive guidance on issues related to same-gender attraction." (Excerpt from interview with Kevin Miyasaki, Vice President of Student Services and Activities with the Scroll on April 28, 2012)</p>
<p><strong>Links</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>LDS Church Web Site - <a href="http://www.lds.org/topics/same-gender-attraction">www.lds.org/topics/same-gender-attraction</a></li>
<li>BYUI Counseling Center - www.byui.edu/counseling-center/self-help/same-gender-attraction</li>
</ul>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x36320" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x36315" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl" Expanded="false"/></Content>
